Repeat: Skip 2 stitches and insert needle as if to knit into the front of the third stitch. Then taking the point of the needle over the front of the 2 skipped stitches and around to the right, catch the yarn and knit. Then slip the third stitch over the 2 skipped stitches and off the needle. Do not slip the 2 skipped stitches off the needle; k2, p2
